Package org.neo4j.common

Interface TokenNameLookup

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    Token, TokenRead
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    InMemoryTokens, KernelToken, TokenHolders
    public interface TokenNameLookup
    Lookup of names from token ids. Tokens are mostly referred to by ids throughout several abstractions. Sometimes token names are required, this is a way to lookup names in those cases.
